hpnicfDvpn.name: hpnicfDvpn
hpnicfDvpn.description: This MIB is Dynamic Virtual Private Network(Dvpn) mib. This MIB is applicable to router. Some objects in this may be used only for some specific products, so users should refer to the related documents to acquire more detail information.

DvpnAlgorithmSuite.name: DvpnAlgorithmSuite
DvpnAlgorithmSuite.description: 13 kinds of dvpn algorithms. encryption method | hash method | key width. dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: des | md5 | 768 dvpnDesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: des | md5 | 1024 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: des | sha1 | 768 dvpnDesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: des | sha1 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: 3des | md5 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: 3des | md5 | 1024 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp768: 3des | sha1 | 768 dvpn3DesCbcSha1PreShaModp1024: 3des | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp768: Aes | md5 | 768 dvpnAesCbcMd5PreShaModp1024: Aes | md5 | 1024 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp768: Aes | sha1 | 768 dvpnAesCbcSHA1Sha1PreShaModp1024: Aes | sha1 | 1024 dvpnAlgorithmNone: none | none | no key

DvpnCommunicateType.name: DvpnCommunicateType
DvpnCommunicateType.description: The type of the communication between client and server. It indicates the direction of the communication.

hpnicfDvpnServiceEnable.name: hpnicfDvpnServiceEnable
hpnicfDvpnServiceEnable.description: Dvpn service enable or disable. If dvpn service is 'disable', dvpn service can not be used.

hpnicfDvpnClassNumber.name: hpnicfDvpnClassNumber
hpnicfDvpnClassNumber.description: The number of dvpn classes. It is only used on client.

hpnicfDvpnClientNumber.name: hpnicfDvpnClientNumber
hpnicfDvpnClientNumber.description: The number of clients which register on the server. When a session of server to client type is built, add 1 to the value of this node. It is only used on server.

hpnicfDvpnMapAgeTime.name: hpnicfDvpnMapAgeTime
hpnicfDvpnMapAgeTime.description: Dvpn map age time, the unit is second. It is only used on server.

hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterInterval.name: hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterInterval
hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterInterval.description: The length of time between the registering of client, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterDumb.name: hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterDumb
hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterDumb.description: The length of time when client dumbs, the unit is second. It is only used on client.

hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterRetry.name: hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterRetry
hpnicfDvpnClientRegisterRetry.description: Regist retry times of client after register fail. It is only used on client.

hpnicfDvpnDropPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDropPkt
hpnicfDvpnDropPkt.description: The number of packets have been droped.

hpnicfDvpnOutputPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnOutputPkt
hpnicfDvpnOutputPkt.description: The number of packets have been sent.

hpnicfDvpnOutputErrorPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnOutputErrorPkt
hpnicfDvpnOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets.

hpnicfDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnEncryptErrorPkt
hpnicfDvpnEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of packets have been encrypted wrongly.

hpnicfDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.name: hpnicfDvpnCurrentDeviceRole
hpnicfDvpnCurrentDeviceRole.description: The current role of the device. The value is decided by the configuration of the tunnel-interface.

hpnicfDvpnSessionNumber.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionNumber
hpnicfDvpnSessionNumber.description: The number of dvpn sessiones including the session of all states.

hpnicfDvpnServerPreSharedKey.name: hpnicfDvpnServerPreSharedKey
hpnicfDvpnServerPreSharedKey.description: The pre-shared-key of server. It is only used on server.

hpnicfDvpnMapTrapEnable.name: hpnicfDvpnMapTrapEnable
hpnicfDvpnMapTrapEnable.description: Dvpn map trap enable or disable.

hpnicfDvpnSessionTrapEnable.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionTrapEnable
hpnicfDvpnSessionTrapEnable.description: Dvpn session trap enable or disable.

hpnicfDvpnClearDomainAllConection.name: hpnicfDvpnClearDomainAllConection
hpnicfDvpnClearDomainAllConection.description: Clear all dvpn conects in the domain, the parameter is the id of the domain.

hpnicfDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.name: hpnicfDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo
hpnicfDvpnClearDvpnStaInfo.description: Clear the statistic information of dvpn.

hpnicfDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.name: hpnicfDvpnTotalRedirectNumber
hpnicfDvpnTotalRedirectNumber.description: The number of redirect packets. It is only used on server.

hpnicfDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.name: hpnicfDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType
hpnicfDvpnGlobalAuthenClientType.description: Dvpn global authentication type being used by server to client. The value is decided by the configuration by the user.

hpnicfDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.name: hpnicfDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain
hpnicfDvpnGlobalUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn global AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which is used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

hpnicfDvpnLocalDeviceId.name: hpnicfDvpnLocalDeviceId
hpnicfDvpnLocalDeviceId.description: The device ID, it is a string.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisAgeTime
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisAgeTime.description: The age-time of the hpnicfDvpnSessionHisTable table. The unit is hour.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisReset.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisReset
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisReset.description: The reset flag of dvpn hpnicfDvpnSessionHisTable table.

hpnicfDvpnPolicyTable.name: hpnicfDvpnPolicyTable
hpnicfDvpnPolicyTable.description: The dvpn policy table. It is used on dvpn server.

hpnicfDvpnPoAuthenClientType.name: hpnicfDvpnPoAuthenClientType
hpnicfDvpnPoAuthenClientType.description: The authentication type used by server to client. The value is decided by the policy configuration of the user. The default value is none.

hpnicfDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.name: hpnicfDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite
hpnicfDvpnPoSessionAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used when session is created.

hpnicfDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.name: hpnicfDvpnPoSessionIdleTime
hpnicfDvpnPoSessionIdleTime.description: The session idle time, the unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.name: hpnicfDvpnPoSessionKeepTime
hpnicfDvpnPoSessionKeepTime.description: The session keepalive time, the unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.name: hpnicfDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval
hpnicfDvpnPoSessionSetupInterval.description: The session setup interval time, the unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.name: hpnicfDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite
hpnicfDvpnPoDataAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the session for createing ipsec sa.

hpnicfDvpnPoSaSeconds.name: hpnicfDvpnPoSaSeconds
hpnicfDvpnPoSaSeconds.description: The duration of DVPN IPSec security association. The unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.name: hpnicfDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain
hpnicfDvpnPoUserDefAAADomain.description: Dvpn policy AAA domain of the user. The domain will decide the authentication server which used by the dvpn server to authenticate dvpn client.

hpnicfDvpnPoRefTimes.name: hpnicfDvpnPoRefTimes
hpnicfDvpnPoRefTimes.description: The total times of the policy being used by dvpn.

hpnicfDvpnPoRowStatus.name: hpnicfDvpnPoRowStatus
hpnicfDvpnPoRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. We support the characteristic of active(1),createAndGo(4),destroy(6).

hpnicfDvpnDomainSessionNum.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainSessionNum
hpnicfDvpnDomainSessionNum.description: The number of session in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainRedirectNum.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainRedirectNum
hpnicfDvpnDomainRedirectNum.description: The number of redirect packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainInputPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainInputPkt
hpnicfDvpnDomainInputPkt.description: The number of input packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainDropPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainDropPkt
hpnicfDvpnDomainDropPkt.description: The number of drop packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputPkt
hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputPkt.description: The number of output packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt
hpnicfDvpnDomainOutputErrorPkt.description: The number of output error packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt
hpnicfDvpnDomainEncryptErrorPkt.description: The number of encrypt error packets in this dvpn domain.

hpnicfDvpnClassTable.name: hpnicfDvpnClassTable
hpnicfDvpnClassTable.description: The Dvpn class table. It is only used on dvpn client.

hpnicfDvpnClassName.name: hpnicfDvpnClassName
hpnicfDvpnClassName.description: The dvpn class name. It is the index of hpnicfDvpnClassTable.

hpnicfDvpnClServerPublicIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnClServerPublicIpType
hpnicfDvpnClServerPublicIpType.description: Dvpn server public ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

hpnicfDvpnClServerPriIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnClServerPriIpType
hpnicfDvpnClServerPriIpType.description: Dvpn server private ip type (ipv4, ipv6).

hpnicfDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.name: hpnicfDvpnClAlgorithmSuite
hpnicfDvpnClAlgorithmSuite.description: The algorithm suite used by the client when sending registry packets to the server. 'dvpnAlgorithmNone' is not supported here.

hpnicfDvpnClAuthenServerType.name: hpnicfDvpnClAuthenServerType
hpnicfDvpnClAuthenServerType.description: The authentication type being used by client to server. The value is decided by the class configuration of the user. The default value is none.

hpnicfDvpnClPreShareKey.name: hpnicfDvpnClPreShareKey
hpnicfDvpnClPreShareKey.description: Dvpn PreShareKey. It is used when the method used by client when authenticating server is pre-share-key, only when the value of the key is the same as that on the server, the client can authenticate server successfully.

hpnicfDvpnClUserName.name: hpnicfDvpnClUserName
hpnicfDvpnClUserName.description: Dvpn UserName. It is configured by the user.

hpnicfDvpnClPasswd.name: hpnicfDvpnClPasswd
hpnicfDvpnClPasswd.description: Dvpn password. It is configured by the user.

hpnicfDvpnClassRowStatus.name: hpnicfDvpnClassRowStatus
hpnicfDvpnClassRowStatus.description: The status of this conceptual row. Only 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy' are supported.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelInterfaceType
hpnicfDvpnTunnelInterfaceType.description: The type of dvpn tunnel (client or server).

hpnicfDvpnTunnelAcl.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelAcl
hpnicfDvpnTunnelAcl.description: The security acl used by the tunnel. If a packet permits the rules, it will not be encrypted.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelClientRegType.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelClientRegType
hpnicfDvpnTunnelClientRegType.description: The register type used by the client . Only the interface type is client, it can be used. undistributed: If a client send a packet to the client with this configuration, setver will only forward the packet whitout sending redirect packets. forward: The client with this configuration will only send packets forwarded by server, which means it can not initiate to build a session with other clients. undistributedandforward: The client with this configuration have the characteristics of both 'forward' and 'undistributed'. normal: The client with this configuration can build session with other clients without any restriction.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelDvpnId.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelDvpnId
hpnicfDvpnTunnelDvpnId.description: The dvpn ID used by the tunnel. The dvpn ID is 0 means that user does not configure dvpn ID. User can not configure a dvpn ID with 0.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelPolicy.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelPolicy
hpnicfDvpnTunnelPolicy.description: The dvpn policy used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is server, it can be used.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelClass.name: hpnicfDvpnTunnelClass
hpnicfDvpnTunnelClass.description: The dvpn class used by the tunnel. Only the interface type is client, it can be used.

hpnicfDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.name: hpnicfDvpnMapPeerDeviceId
hpnicfDvpnMapPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

hpnicfDvpnMapDvpnId.name: hpnicfDvpnMapDvpnId
hpnicfDvpnMapDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the map belongs to. The dvpn ID is 0 means that the map has not been built. It has not gotten the dvpn ID at that time.

hpnicfDvpnMapBuildTime.name: hpnicfDvpnMapBuildTime
hpnicfDvpnMapBuildTime.description: The time of the map created, the unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIpType
hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIp.name: hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIp
hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of map peer device.

hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType
hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map peer device.

hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.name: hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIp
hpnicfDvpnMapPeerPublicIp.description: The public ip of map peer device.

hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIpType
hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIp.name: hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIp
hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of map local device.

hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType
hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of map local device.

hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.name: hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIp
hpnicfDvpnMapLocalPublicIp.description: The public ip of map local device.

hpnicfDvpnMapUserName.name: hpnicfDvpnMapUserName
hpnicfDvpnMapUserName.description: The user name used by the client registering to server. If the client is not been authenticated, this is a null string.

hpnicfDvpnMapUdpPort.name: hpnicfDvpnMapUdpPort
hpnicfDvpnMapUdpPort.description: The udp port used by map peer device.

hpnicfDvpnMapType.name: hpnicfDvpnMapType
hpnicfDvpnMapType.description: The type of the map. 'clientToclient' is not supported here.

hpnicfDvpnMapState.name: hpnicfDvpnMapState
hpnicfDvpnMapState.description: mapClientInit: The client initiates the map. mapClientBegin: The client begins the process of registering to the server. mapClientAlgreq: The client requests to negotiate the algorithm. mapClientKexReq: The client requests to negotiate the key. mapClientAuthenReq: The client sends authentication information to the server. mapClientConfigReq: The client requests to get some configuration information from the server. Do not support now. mapClientReq: The client requests to register to the server. mapClientSuccess: The client registers to the server successfully. mapServerBegin: The server begins the process of receive a new register. mapServerAlgorithm:The sever begins to negotiate Algorithm. mapServerKexInit: The server replys to the algorithm negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to negotiate key. mapServerAuthenInit: The server replys to the key negotiation packet from the client successfully and begin to authenticate client, in the case of the authentication-client method is not none. mapServerConfigInit: The server send some configuration information to client. Do not support now. mapServerInit: The server replys to the authentication packet from the client successfully and begin to receive client information. mapServerFinished: The server receives client information successfully.

hpnicfDvpnSessionDvpnId.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionDvpnId
hpnicfDvpnSessionDvpnId.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIp.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIp
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPriIp.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerDeviceId.description: The device ID of session peer device. It is a string.

hpnicfDvpnSessionBuildTime.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionBuildTime
hpnicfDvpnSessionBuildTime.description: The time of the Session being built, the unit is second.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIp
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerPubIp.description: The public ip of session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType
hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIpType.description: The public ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIp
hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPubIp.description: The public ip of session local device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType
hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIpType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session local device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIp
hpnicfDvpnSessionLocalPriIp.description: The private ip of session local device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerUdpPort.description: The udp port used by session peer device .

hpnicfDvpnSessionUserName.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionUserName
hpnicfDvpnSessionUserName.description: The user's name. If the session type is client to client, the value of this object is a null string.

hpnicfDvpnSessionState.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionState
hpnicfDvpnSessionState.description: The state of the session. sessionSetupInit: The initiation of the session. sessionSetupReq: The initiator requests to negotiate the SA and so on of the session. sessionSetupSuccess: The session has been built successfully. sessionRekeyReq: The initiator requests to renegotiate the SA. sessionRekeyRep: The passive side replies with a SA renegotiation response packet successfully.

hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerType
hpnicfDvpnSessionPeerType.description: The type of the session peer device. It may be client software or a router.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisTable.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisTable
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisTable.description: The dvpn session history table. This table contains session's history information, include input/output packet number, up/down time, etc. This table will exist during the 'hpnicfDvpnSessionHisAgeTime'.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisDvpnID
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisDvpnID.description: The ID of the dvpn domain which the session belongs to.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIPType.description: The private ip type (ipv4, ipv6) of session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerPriIP.description: The private ip of the session peer device.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisSendPkt
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisSendPkt.description: The number of sent packets on the session.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisRcvPkt.description: The number of received packets on the session.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineNumber.description: The number of the session online.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisOnlineFlag.description: If the session is online, the value is 'yes'. If the session is not online, the value is 'no'.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisPeerDeviceId.description: The identifier of peer device. It is a string.

hpnicfDvpnMibCompliance.name: hpnicfDvpnMibCompliance
hpnicfDvpnMibCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement the DVPN MIB.

hpnicfDvpnGlobalGroup.name: hpnicfDvpnGlobalGroup
hpnicfDvpnGlobalGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn global information.

hpnicfDvpnPolicyGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn policy information.

hpnicfDvpnDomainInfoGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn domain information.

hpnicfDvpnClassGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn class information.

hpnicfDvpnTunnelGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn tunnel interface information.

hpnicfDvpnMapGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn map information.

hpnicfDvpnSessionGroup.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionGroup
hpnicfDvpnSessionGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn session information.

hpnicfDvpnSessionHisGroup.name: hpnicfDvpnSessionHisGroup
hpnicfDvpnSessionHisGroup.description: A collection of objects providing dvpn session history information.
